    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Technique of pattern bond using only stretchers and in which the vertical joints of one course fall midway between the joints of the courses above and below.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
